 (x+y=500)*3 = 3x+3y = 1500 \\ (0.70x + 0.30y = 0.60)*10 = 7x+3y=6 
\require{cancel} \space\space\space\space\space\space\space\space\space3x+\bcancel{3y}\space\space\space=1500\\ - (-7x-(\bcancel{3y})=-6)\\ \_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\\ x = -4x \space\space\space\space\space\space\space\space\space\space\space\space\space\space\space= 1494\\ x = \frac{-4x}{-4} = \frac{1494}{-4} \\ x = \frac{1494}{-4} = -373.5 
